\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Control-comparison overview of the March 30 frozen bundle. The upper-left panel ranks all controllers by mean Sharpe, where \texttt  {D+} leads, plain \texttt  {D} remains the strongest non-extension baseline, and the MLP meta-controller is the strongest learned challenger. The remaining panels summarize return--drawdown trade-offs, the best method in each controller family, and Sharpe stability across train fractions.}}{12}{figure.caption.9}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:control_overview}{{2}{12}{Control-comparison overview of the March 30 frozen bundle. The upper-left panel ranks all controllers by mean Sharpe, where \texttt {D+} leads, plain \texttt {D} remains the strongest non-extension baseline, and the MLP meta-controller is the strongest learned challenger. The remaining panels summarize return--drawdown trade-offs, the best method in each controller family, and Sharpe stability across train fractions}{figure.caption.9}{}}
